| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4704 — Recovery Inhibition (noescape)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2e5419c9-aaf4-5701-b2c9-5377f68509dc"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
